rule.display_format:
【检定：{行动类型}】
随机值: {raw_roll}
修正: {character_mod} + {situational_mod}
最终值: {total}
目标值: {dc}
结果: {success_level}

memory_schema.template:
```json
{
  "_meta": {
    "version": "1.0",
    "updated_at": "{YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM}",
    "session_id": 1,
    "rule_mode": "平衡模式"
  },
  "player": {
    "name": "{角色名}",
    "identity": "{职业/身份/背景}",
    "level": 1,
    "traits": ["{特质1}"]
  },
  "abilities": {
    "power": 0,
    "agility": 0,
    "insight": 0,
    "will": 0,
    "charm": 0,
    "craft": 0
  },
  "resources": {
    "hp_current": 10,
    "hp_max": 10,
    "stamina": 5,
    "focus": 5,
    "currency": 0,
    "status_effects": []
  },
  "inventory": {
    "items": [{"name": "{物品名}", "qty": 1, "note": "{备注}"}],
    "key_items": []
  },
  "quests": {
